            <lg xml:id="TK1318">
<l>tummuc ceṟuppa vaḻutā ṇumaruḷḷa </l>
<l>lemmai maṟaittirō veṉṟu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>When I suppressed my sneezing, she wept saying, "I suppose you (did so) to hide from me your own people's remembrance of you".</l>
